1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:10,077
Didn’t stretch, didn’t warm up much

2
00:00:10,227 --> 00:00:15,304
Held the racket like a coffee cup

3
00:00:15,454 --> 00:00:20,531
Coach said try to find your spell

4
00:00:20,681 --> 00:00:25,759
Just breathe and swing and hope it fell

5
00:00:25,909 --> 00:00:30,986
Underhand serve, yeah that’s my call

6
00:00:31,136 --> 00:00:36,213
Not fast, not tricky — but it beats them
all

7
00:00:36,363 --> 00:00:41,440
They swing too wild or let it go

8
00:00:41,590 --> 00:00:46,667
I win the point just keeping it low

9
00:00:46,817 --> 00:00:51,894
School van hums as we head out

10
00:00:52,044 --> 00:00:57,121
No one cheers, but we don’t doubt

11
00:00:57,271 --> 00:01:02,349
Somewhere out there, we pretend to hear

12
00:01:02,499 --> 00:01:07,576
A quiet roar from Brooks the Bear

13
00:01:07,726 --> 00:01:12,803
Mostly we walk around picking up balls

14
00:01:12,953 --> 00:01:18,030
Crocs squeak loud in the quiet of it all

15
00:01:18,180 --> 00:01:23,257
No crowd, no stats on a wall

16
00:01:23,407 --> 00:01:28,484
Just one more serve, Crocs and all

17
00:01:28,634 --> 00:01:33,711
Coach says I’m the most chill on the team

18
00:01:33,861 --> 00:01:38,939
Even when it’s match point, I don’t scream

19
00:01:39,089 --> 00:01:44,166
I just stand there, take my time

20
00:01:44,316 --> 00:01:49,393
Hit it in and everything’s fine

21
00:01:49,543 --> 00:01:54,620
Mostly we walk around picking up balls

22
00:01:54,770 --> 00:01:59,847
Lose track of score, forget who falls

23
00:01:59,997 --> 00:02:05,074
I’m not great — but I don’t stall

24
00:02:05,224 --> 00:02:10,301
Second serve, Crocs and all

25
00:02:10,451 --> 00:02:15,529
Parents wait in the lot, quiet and kind

26
00:02:15,679 --> 00:02:20,756
Wave as we wander off the backline

27
00:02:20,906 --> 00:02:25,983
It’s not for glory, not for a call

28
00:02:26,133 --> 00:02:31,210
We just keep showing up — Crocs and all
